title: Enchanté
overview: Enchanté is a French term that means "nice to meet you." But what is Theo supposed to do when four men claim to be the Enchanté he's looking for?Theo, a dashing young man who recently returned from France, is on a journey to find the real Enchanté with the assistance of his childhood friend Akk, who lives just across the street. The two of them are drawn by the mission to meet with these four ideal gentlemen:Natee, a third-year talented artist from the Faculty of Fine and Applied Arts.Phupha, a third-year academically outstanding student from the Faculty of Liberal Arts.Saifa, a third-year music genius from the Faculty of Communication Arts.And Wayo, a third-year football team captain from the Faculty of Sports Science.Who is going to be the final answer to this love? Hang tight and find out together.
